            "children": [
              "How to Play"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "title"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-3"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Arrange all 7 tangram pieces to fill the target silhouette on the table."
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "text"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-4"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Keyboard Controls"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "section"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-5"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Click a piece to select it. Arrows/WASD to move. Q/E to rotate 45 degrees. F to flip the parallelogram. Tab to cycle pieces. H for a hint. Z to undo. R to restart. Esc to pause."
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "text"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-6"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "XR Controls"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "section"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-7"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Point and click to select pieces. Thumbstick to move/rotate. A/X to flip. B/Y to pause."
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "text"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-8"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Game Modes"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "section"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-9"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Classic: Solve at your own pace. Speed: 2-minute time limit. Zen: No timer, no pressure. Challenge: Limited to 50 moves."
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "text"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-10"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Tips"
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "section"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-11"
          },
          {
            "sourceTag": "text",
            "type": "custom",
            "children": [
              "Pieces snap when close to correct position + rotation. Use hints when stuck -- they cost 1 move. Start with Easy puzzles to learn piece shapes."
            ],
            "properties": {
              "class": "text"
            },
            "dataUid": "uid-12"
          },
